<article id="post-768499" class="post-768499 digital-library type-digital-library status-publish has-post-thumbnail hentry category-architecture-and-hardware category-computing-applications category-systems-and-networking issue-july-2025 section-sustainability-and-computing">

			
<header class="article-header article-header--default">
	<div class="article-header__inner container">
		<div class="article-header__section"><a href="https://cacm.acm.org/section/sustainability-and-computing/">Sustainability and Computing</a></div>
		<div class="article-header__topic-and-issue-section">
			<span class="article-header__topic">
			<a href="https://cacm.acm.org/category/architecture-and-hardware/">Architecture and Hardware</a>			</span>
			<span class="article-header__issue-section">
							</span>
		</div>
		<h1 class="article-header__title">Energy-Optimized Supercomputer Networks Using Wind Energy</h1>
					<div class="article-header__subtitle"><p>Operating high-performance compute nodes among wind farms would increase computing sustainability by maximizing renewable electric energy usage and minimizing energy waste.</p>
</div>
		
		<div class="article-header__meta">
			<div class="article-header__byline">
				By <a href="https://cacm.acm.org/author/alexander-kilian/" title="Posts by Alexander Kilian" class="author url fn" rel="author">Alexander Kilian</a>, <a href="https://cacm.acm.org/author/hermann-de-meer/" title="Posts by Hermann de Meer" class="author url fn" rel="author">Hermann de Meer</a>, and <a href="https://cacm.acm.org/author/gunnar-schomaker/" title="Posts by Gunnar Schomaker" class="author url fn" rel="author">Gunnar Schomaker</a>			</div>
			<div class="article-header__posted-on">
				<span class="posted-on">Posted <time datetime="2025-06-20T11:01:17-04:00">Jun 20 2025</time></span>			</div>
		</div>

			<figure class="article-header__figure">
			<div class="image-wrapper image-wrapper--widescreen"><img width="1024" height="576" src="https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/061225.RSS_.Energy-Optimized-G.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full" alt="wind turbines" loading="eager" decoding="async" srcset="https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/061225.RSS_.Energy-Optimized-G.jpg 2180w, https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/061225.RSS_.Energy-Optimized-G.jpg?resize=300,169 300w, https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/061225.RSS_.Energy-Optimized-G.jpg?resize=768,432 768w, https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/061225.RSS_.Energy-Optimized-G.jpg?resize=1024,576 1024w, https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/061225.RSS_.Energy-Optimized-G.jpg?resize=1536,864 1536w, https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/061225.RSS_.Energy-Optimized-G.jpg?resize=2048,1152 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></div>		</figure>

		<div class="article-header__share">
			
